OL,5, A hosepipe and sprinkler ban is being  
OL,6, imposed on people in Kent and Sussex.  
OL,8,FSouth East Water said it had no choice 
OL,9,Fafter demand for drinking water had    
OL,10,Freached "record levels" in June,       
OL,11,Fsimilar to last year's drought.        
OL,13,FSome households in Kent and Sussex have
OL,14,Fbeen without water since Monday due to 
OL,15,Fsupply issues.                         
OL,17,FEarlier this week, the water company   
OL,18,Furged people to only use water for     
OL,19,Fessential purposes. It will impose the 
OL,20,Fban on hosepipes from 26 June.         
